  * Bug #1160: FD leaks causing a spam of accept() failed messages
  * Bug #1168: web: duplicate device detected when editing some camera settings
  * Bug #1174: Storage deletion routine does not delete files on second and subsequent storage paths
  * Fixed an installation bug on debian systems with modified USERGROUPS_ENAB

