 -- Curtis Hall <curt@bluecherry.net>  Wed, 24 Nov 2010 14:58:26 -0600

bluecherry (2.0.0-0beta1-5) lucid; urgency=low

  * This release incorporates beta1-4 changes (which was accidently made public, so some customers downloaded it - this the reason for the bump) along with these issues:

  * Bug #498: Server respawning in an endless loop
  * Bug #500: PHP Warning: SQLite3::query(): Unable to prepare statement: 1, unrecognized token: "0x00000002" in /usr/share/bluecherry/www/lib/lib.php on line 66
  * Bug #501: bc-detect showing other V4L devices
  * Bug #507: [Critical] Unable to playback events
  * Bug #509: [Critical] bc-server generating 584byte video files
  * Bug #510: MJPEG feed breaks, causing video weirdness on random ports
  * Bug #511: Error writing frame to outfile: Input/output error
  * Bug #513: bc-server segfaults and CPU soft locks
  * Bug #516: Web: Password changes do not take affect
  * Bug #518: Limit image width for motion mapping
  * Bug #519: bc-server crashes with E(1): asoundlib failed
  * Bug #520: audio_channels are not being added to the database
  * Feature #521: Add error logging for bc_alsa_open

  * Full list: http://improve.bluecherrydvr.com/versions/show/51

 -- Curtis Hall <curt@bluecherry.net>  Thu, 18 Nov 2010 16:56:50 -0600

bluecherry (2.0.0-0beta1-4) lucid; urgency=low

  * server: Detect invalid audio_format in db
  * Web: Use integer value, not string literal value when setting audio_format

 -- Curtis Hall <curt@bluecherry.net>  Sun, 14 Nov 2010 09:39:48 -0600

bluecherry (2.0.0-0beta1-3) lucid; urgency=low

  * debian: Stop old bc-server init script on preinst
  * debian: Use cat, not zcat

 -- Ben Collins <bcollins@bluecherry.net>  Sat, 13 Nov 2010 16:02:50 -0500

bluecherry (2.0.0-0beta1-2) lucid; urgency=low

  * Remove old init scripts
  * Added defaults for audio volume and video controls

 -- Ben Collins <bcollins@bluecherry.net>  Fri, 12 Nov 2010 16:02:50 -0500

bluecherry (2.0.0-0beta1-1) lucid; urgency=low

  * bc-detect: Insert card_id into AvailableSources
  * lib: Reduce buffers to 16 for mpeg and 2 for mjpeg
  * update.php: show device name to set a unique name
  * Recommend solo6010-dkms (#467)
  * log: Create log files as syslog.bluecherry (#469)
  * Add udev rules to automatically run bc-detect on solo module load (#470)

 -- Ben Collins <bcollins@bluecherry.net>  Fri, 12 Nov 2010 11:30:50 -0500

bluecherry (2.0.0-0beta1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Initial packaging

 -- Ben Collins <bcollins@bluecherry.net>  Mon, 19 Apr 2010 11:45:30 -0400
